  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the garlic, turmeric, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the pita bread and cook for 2-3 minutes, stirring frequently, until lightly browned.",
    "Add the parsley, cilantro, and mint. Cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Pour in the lemon juice and cook for 1 minute, stirring frequently.",
    "Serve warm or at room temperature.",
    "Adjust seasoning as needed."
